{"tid":1681052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次運動造成的經濟損失，仲少過颱風山竹","createTime":"2019-10-29T07:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T03:24:20.000Z","uid":149978,"like":353,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"2c54e1ce1f015dc396b5fefe50b98e5866b8150d","tid":1681052,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>連一個十號風球都不如</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2959760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2959760&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=7c8b8341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2959760&h=b2fc35a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2959760</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕香港反送中抗爭持續不停，並已對香港地鐵、中企相關企業財產造成破壞，有保險業專家指出，和抗爭中包括縱火、人為破壞等抗議活動造成的業務損失理賠，可能<strong>已達近6億港元（約新台幣23.6億元），創香港史上第3高，</strong>而僅是港鐵公司就可能提出達1億港元的理賠。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》今（28）報導，對香港反送中抗爭造成的業務損失等保險理賠，已達近6億港元，超越了SARS時期的3.25億港元，創香港史上第3高。<strong>而據香港保險業聯會數據，去年侵襲香港的強颱山竹造成的索賠，總額達31億港元，2017年襲港的天鴿颱風，索賠總額為8.58億港元。</strong>"},{"pid":"f86b253dc2b293c3fcf91c1d674a7ce26a25ce99","tid":1681052,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770747a50331b9cbaf3b26836aeb1d3c271bb1ea","tid":1681052,"uid":161374,"like":75,"dislike":13,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"不嬲天災都係勁過人....好出奇？"},{"pid":"403d564a2e86b2500385eb91ceac715d6291c22a","tid":1681052,"uid":2843,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"quote":{"pid":"2c54e1ce1f015dc396b5fefe50b98e5866b8150d","tid":1681052,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:27:49